condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I, A.2 | Description :HBOR will monitor project performance in accordance with theOperationalManual. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A.1 | Description :HBOR, shall maintain, until the completion of the Project, the PIU,and ensure that the PIU functions at all times in a manner and with staffing and budgetary resources satisfactory to the Bank andsuitable to enable it to implement the Project, including compliance under the Project with all of the Bank's fiduciary andsafeguard requirements. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A.3 | Description :The Borrower shall submit, not later than August 15 and June 30,respectively, a compliance certificate confirming ongoing compliance with the laws and regulations of the Guarantor applicable tothe Borrower and providing information on agreed-upon prudential ratios, as certified by the Borrower's management on a semi-annualbasis as of June 30 and December 31 of each fiscal year. | Frequency :SemiAnnual

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A.4b, Section I. B | Description :HBOR shall relend to each Participating Bank a portionof the proceeds of the Loan under a Subsidiary Loan Agreement to be entered into between the Borrower and each PB, under terms andconditions which shall have been approved by the Bank, and which shall include without limitation, those set forth in paragraphsB.2, B.3, B.4 and B.5 of Section I.B of Schedule 2 to the Loan Agreement. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. A.5 | Description :Borrower shall be entitled to make Sub-loans directly to BeneficiaryEnterprises under the same terms and conditions as PBs pursuant to Section I. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. B.5a. | Description :PFIs shall undertake to carry out activities under the Project inaccordance with appropriate financial standards and practices, including the provisions of the Anti Corruption Guidelinesapplicable to recipients of Loan proceeds other than the Borrower, with adequate qualified management and staff and in conformitywith the investment and lending policies in the Operational Manual. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. B.5b, Section I. C | Description :PFIs shall provide, promptly as needed, the funds,facilities, services and other resources required for the purpose; and make Sub-loans to Beneficiary Enterprises on the terms andconditions set forth in the Operational Manual, including, without limitation, the terms and conditions set forth in Section I.C ofSchedule 2 to the Loan Agreement. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section I. C.5 | Description :Sub-loans shall be made for Sub-projects which are each determined, onthe basis of an appraisal carried out in accordance with procedures acceptable to the Bank set forth in the Operational Manual. |Frequency :CONTINUOUS
Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B.1 | Description :HBOR will maintain a financial management system acceptable to theBank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B.2 | Description :HBOR shall prepare and furnish not later than 45 days after the endof each calendar semester, interim unaudited financial reports. | Frequency :Quarterly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B.3 | Description :HBOR shall submit annual audited financial statements, independentauditor's report and management recommendation letter. The annual audited financial statements and the audit reports will beprovided within 6 months of the end of each fiscal year. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II. A.1 | Description :The project financial reports, including the Summary of Expenditures,and Designated Account Statements will be audited by independent auditors acceptable to the Bank and on terms of referenceacceptable to the Bank. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II. C.b and C.c | Description :HBOR shall prepare and furnish to the Bank, on or aboutSeptember 1 2011, a report integrating the results of the monitoring and evaluation activities under the Project and shall reviewwith the Bank, on or about November 1, 2011 such report, and, thereafter, all measures required to ensure the efficient completionof the Project and the achievement of the objectives thereof. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sections I and II | Description :HBOR shall implement credit lines in accordance with the provisionsof the Loan Agreement and Operational Manual, including the eligibility criteria for PFIs and Beneficiary Enterprises, agreed uponterms and conditions for on lending and monitoring and reporting requirements. | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
